name: CSSKeyframesRule
description: The CSSKeyframesRule interface describes an object representing a complete set of keyframes for a CSS animation. It corresponds to the contents of a whole @keyframes at-rule. It implements the CSSRule interface with a type value of 7 (CSSRule.KEYFRAMES_RULE).
